            <p><strong>The Music Network</strong> is community-driven and learns from your playlists.</p>

            <ul>
            <li><strong>Database.</strong> Cassandra is used to as high-throughput enterprise database for processing data uploads from all over the world. </li>
			<li><strong>Analytics.</strong> Hadoop jobs run in the background to find affinity relationships between artists.</li>
			<li><strong>Search.</strong> A powerful index is kept up to date as new playlists are uploaded, allowing for fast-searching on artist name.</li>
